article_title: Aetna To Stop Selling Obamacare Plans In Two States And D.C. For 2016

article_metadata.description: Aetna said it will no longer offer subsidized health insurance benefits in two states and Washington, D.C. where it currently sells products on government-run exchanges under the Affordable Care Act. For 2016, Aetna said it will no longer offer individual exchange plans in Washington, D.C., Utah and Kansas. It added Kentucky [...]
